{
  "texts": [
    "Individual evaluation of long-form answers.",
    "Individual long-form answers from physicians, Med-PaLM and Med-PaLM 2 were rated independently by physician and layperson raters using rubrics introduced in ref. 1.",
    "Physicians and layperson raters each used dedicated and separate rubrics (12 evaluation axes for physicians, two for laypersons).",
    "Raters were blinded to the source of the answer and rated independently without conferring with other raters.",
    "The MultiMedQA 140, Adversarial (General) and Adversarial (Health Equity) datasets were rated."
  ]
}